import "../styles/DetailedForecast.scss" const DetailedForecast = (props) => { const allWeatherItems = props.forecast.data[0].weather.map( element => { return
{element.main}
} ) return (
{allWeatherItems}
{"Temperature"}
{props.forecast.data[0].main.temp}
{"Feels Like"}
{props.forecast.data[0].main.feels_like}
{"Atmospheric Pressure"}
{props.forecast.data[0].main.grnd_level}
{"Humidity"}
{props.forecast.data[0].main.humidity}
{"Clouds Coverage"}
{props.forecast.data[0].clouds.all}
) } export default DetailedForecast
